  "title": "Events & Marketing Representative",
  "description": "<p>We are being appointed by local and international clientele from diversified markets to build strength and increase public awareness of their presence and services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are looking for a way to get into the marketing sector and represent some of the most well-known companies, we invite you to explore opportunity as a Project Marketing Lead. Our rapid expansion necessitates the addition of more brains and hustlers!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibility:</p>\n<p>a) Conduct sales and marketing strategies through various channels alignment with strategic in able to link customers with the suitable core market.</p>\n<p>b) Increase sales income by providing on-site assistance for all projects.</p>\n<p>c) Support and enhance the team's growth, along with handling the sales and operations</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<p>a) Have an insatiable desire for success</p>\n<p>b) Have a positive attitude toward learning.</p>\n<p>c) Appreciate teamwork and have good communication skills</p>\n<p>d) Customer engagement experience will be a plus.</p>",
